.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-agnetha-faltskog-suspicious-abba-voyage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-agnetha-faltskog-suspicious-abba-voyage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-agnetha-faltskog-suspicious-abba-voyage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-agnetha-faltskog-suspicious-abba-voyage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/agnetha-faltskog">Agnetha Fältskog</a>透露，她早期对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/abba-voyage-live-in-london-review-photos-video-setlist-3235227">ABBA Voyage</a>节目持保留态度，并表示她最初感到“怀疑”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-bjorn-ulvaeus-on-the-future-of-the-voyage-live-show-and-if-theyd-ever-play-glastonbury-3432105">ABBA 的 Björn Ulvaeus 谈论“Voyage”现场表演的未来以及他们是否会参加格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 2017 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/a-virtual-abba-tour-is-set-to-take-place-in-2019-2139797">乐队就宣布将于 2019 年以数字形式重聚</a>。重聚巡演推迟后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-reunion-new-album-tour-show-tickets-3035924">ABBA Voyage 终于宣布于 2021 年 9 月举行</a>。</p><p>这次虚拟巡演在伊丽莎白女王奥林匹克公园专门建造的 ABBA 竞技场取得了巨大成功，被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-bjorn-ulvaeus-on-the-future-of-the-voyage-live-show-and-if-theyd-ever-play-glastonbury-3432105"><em>《NME》</em>描述为“来自美丽新世界的史诗级阿凡达大型组合”</a> ， <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-anniversary-images-tickets-3448556">现已延长至 2024 年</a>。</p><p>然而，Fältskog 透露，她一开始并不完全相信这个想法。这位瑞典歌手兼词曲作家今天发行了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-agnetha-faltskog-returns-with-new-single-where-do-we-go-from-here-and-announces-album-a-3491431">新专辑《A+》</a> ，她在一次新的采访中告诉<em><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2023/oct/13/abba-agnetha-faltskog-music-fame-voyage-icon" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《卫报》</a></em> ：“我必须说，我有点怀疑——你知道，这是什么？”</p><p> “我们整个二月（2020 年）都在努力准备——听起来并不多，但确实是与所有这些技术人员和你身上的所有东西一起表演歌曲。我们非常努力地工作，老实说，我对此感到不太舒服。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="ABBA 谈论他们的 Voyage 现场表演、新音乐以及下一步发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TVZ3SPkWObo?start=1&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “但大概四五天后，你就会开始思考：好吧，我会再去那里。此外，音乐也有帮助，因为它给我们一种非常特别的感觉，一路上我会感到自豪——他们真的很想再次见到我们。”</p><p> Fältskog 补充道，虽然她很享受首演之夜，但她想“像一只小老鼠一样”再次偷偷地看演出。她补充道：“坐在角落里，只是看看。”</p><p>她还赞扬了这次旅行的形式，因为它不需要她亲自到场。 “我躺在家里的床上，同时又在伦敦。做得非常巧妙，不是吗？” </p><figure id="attachment_3514929" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514929" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514929" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022.jpg" alt="（从左至右）Benny Andersson、Agnetha Faltskog、Anni-Frid Lyngstad 和 Björn Ulvaeus" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abba-voyage-photocall-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514929" class="wp-caption-text"> （从左至右）Benny Andersson、Agnetha Faltskog、Anni-Frid Lyngstad 和 Björn Ulvaeus 出席 2022 年 5 月 26 日在英国伦敦 ABBA Arena 举行的《ABBA Voyage》全球首映式（图片来源：David M. Benett/Dave Benett） /盖蒂图片社）</figcaption></figure><p>早在五月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-anniversary-images-tickets-3448556">，ABBA Voyage 就庆祝了首映一周年</a>，组织者通过发布该作品的新图片来纪念这一周年。</p><p> The ABBA Voyage virtual concert series is currently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-residency-to-be-extended-to-november-2023-buy-tickets-3350889">set to run in London into 2024</a> , with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-virtual-concert-experience-world-tour-3407519">plans reported for the experience to be taken on a world tour.</a></p><p> Asked about what the future of the show involves, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-bjorn-ulvaeus-on-the-future-of-the-voyage-live-show-and-if-theyd-ever-play-glastonbury-3432105">ABBA&#39;s Björn Ulvaeus told <em>NME</em> in the summer</a> : “We hope to stay in this [London] venue for as long as we can. We hope they&#39;ll have us for many years, and we might build other replicas of this in other places: Asia, Australia, North America. There are lots and promoters and cities that we&#39;re talking to at the moment about that.</p><p> “Each one would take at least two years to build, but there will be announcements towards the end of this year or the beginning of next about where we actually are going. That&#39;s <em>if</em> we&#39;re going somewhere, which we will.”</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fabba-voyage-tickets%2Fartist%2F5358174" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here for tickets &#39;ABBA Voyage&#39; in London</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-agnetha-faltskog-was-initially-suspicious-of-voyage-show-3514920">ABBA&#39;s Agnetha Fältskog was initially “suspicious” of &#39;Voyage&#39; show</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
